<p>Birth - both parents Indian</p>
<p>Descent - at least one Indian + registered within 1 year + not dual citizenship at 18 years within 6 months</p>
<p>Registration - 7 years+both his parents are registered</p>
<p>Naturalization - (11/14+1 ) + language knowledge + waive off condition for distinguished service</p>
<p>Incorporation of territory -not as a matter of right but when government notifies an order (e.g Pondicherry)</p>
